{"tid":1229860,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【換車的決策】Audi A3 vs MarkX","createTime":"2019-06-16T04:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T09:05:54.000Z","uid":27995,"like":15,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8eeee04c74fd2ab1e76c53c543ed14ee945dea79","tid":1229860,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"近日準備換車，暫時有兩款幾岩自己要求 (4 - 5座 / 房車款)<br />\n主要：日常上班下班（非公路）、假日使用，預計用3 - 5年<br />\n想巴打們比比意見，或者對依兩款有咩評價<br />\n<br />\n1. 2015年左右的 Audi A3 1.4T (房車款)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P15Qiw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP15Qiw0.jpg&h=a11ddac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 2014年左右的 Toyota Mark X <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ji3KnYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJi3KnYF.jpg&h=27a53bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時油耗就應該A3平D，車價對於差唔多年份都係A3平D<br />\n但考慮到會用接近５年，豐田又維修應該平D"},{"pid":"7b8a254903fb32c8d20e604a763c684187d9ea64","tid":1229860,"uid":196924,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"揸成5年就Mark X啦<br />\nMark X保養平 又後驅"},{"pid":"d74ecbd512b7307bd81088306548ed2401baa6d7","tid":1229860,"uid":27995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b8a254903fb32c8d20e604a763c684187d9ea64","tid":1229860,"uid":196924,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:12:19.000Z","msg":"揸成5年就Mark X啦<br />\nMark X保養平 又後驅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"但考慮到基本上日日用車，Mark X 油耗成$2/km <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以先遲遲未決定到 (我都有想過Mark X 保養平)"},{"pid":"3fbd4baef19feba8f176e619247d072b49d34bdb","tid":1229860,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"Mark X 最低都250G喎<br />\n油費可能會高啲<br />\n但個款夠靚仔<br />\n又係後轆車<br />\n不過停咗產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b60425b3cae61aa05e4d2e16a